ActEmployment Insurance Act
SubjectRegulations Amending the Employment Insurance Regulations and the Employment Insurance (Fishing) Regulations
PrecisRegulations Amending the EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE REGULATIONS AND THE EMPLOYMENT INSURANCE (FISHING) REGULATIONS in order to end the different treatment of the New Entrants and Re-Entrants and ensure that they will have the same access to Employment Insurance benefits as the rest of the workforce.
